00:48:24,984 --> 00:48:29,196
I acquired a Canadian mining company.

796
00:48:29,280 --> 00:48:31,532
The plan is to invest 100 billion won
from my group.

797
00:48:31,616 --> 00:48:33,743
If there's no profit in a year

798
00:48:33,826 --> 00:48:35,119
it'll go bankrupt

799
00:48:35,202 --> 00:48:36,579
wasting 100 billion won.

800
00:48:38,539 --> 00:48:40,291
Recommend me
a Commissioner of the National Tax Service

801
00:48:40,374 --> 00:48:42,335
and a Trade, Industry,
and Resources Minister.

802
00:48:42,418 --> 00:48:46,047
And the Environment and Labor Minister.

803
00:48:47,715 --> 00:48:48,758
My, my.

804
00:48:50,468 --> 00:48:51,969
You get more greedy with age.

805
00:48:52,053 --> 00:48:53,721
That greed got you

806
00:48:53,804 --> 00:48:56,390
in that very seat, didn't it?

807
00:48:57,099 --> 00:48:59,060
All the power goes to you

808
00:48:59,143 --> 00:49:01,979
and all the money to me, Jang Yong-hyeon.

